<h1>Before 1947: A gallery of rare pictures</h1>
<hr />
<h2>Take a look at 14 paintings, photographs, and documents on display at the Punjab government’s Archives Department</h2>
<div class="name">
<p>
<a href="../writer/web-desk" target="_blank"> Web Desk</a>
</p>
